components
The selector property here indicates which DOM element this component is going to use. In
this case, any <app-hello-world></app-hello-world> tags that appear within a template will be
compiled using the HelloWorldComponent class and get any attached functionality.

3 @Component({
4 selector: 'app-hello-world', -->using a <app-hello-world>
5 templateUrl: './hello-world.component.html', -->template
6 styleUrls: ['./hello-world.component.css']
7 })

template
We can define templates two ways, either by using the template key in our @Component object or
by specifying a templateUrl.

